Package gg.valgo.gradian.parsers.combinators

Class MaybeParser<ResultType>

  • java.lang.Object
    • gg.valgo.gradian.Parser<ResultType>
      • gg.valgo.gradian.parsers.combinators.MaybeParser<ResultType>
  • Type Parameters:
    ResultType - The result type of the parser.
    public class MaybeParser<ResultType>
extends Parser<ResultType>
    Optionally parses a value, resulting in null if the value could not be matched. This parser will never fail. This parser accepts any type of input.
